<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  <body class="overflow-x-hidden font-poppins box-border bg-[#121a26]">
    <%- include('./partials/nav') %>

    <section
      class="relative w-full py-24 md:py-32 bg-cover bg-center"
      style="background-image: url('/IMAGES/services.webp')"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-60"></div>
      <div
        class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8"
      >
        <h1
          class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold uppercase text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-lg"
        >
          Our <span class="text-red-600">Services</span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md"
        >
          Empowering individuals and organizations to achieve unprecedented
          success through tailored programs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#121a26] py-16 px-5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
          Transforming Potential into
          <span class="text-yellow-400">Performance</span>
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-loose max-w-4xl mx-auto"
        >
          At BS Bhandari, we believe in unlocking the inner greatness of every
          individual and enterprise. Our diverse range of services is
          meticulously crafted to address your unique challenges, foster growth,
          and pave the way for sustainable success. Explore how we can help you
          achieve your highest aspirations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#121a26] py-16 px-5">
      <div
        class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-[#1a2b3a] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="text-[#17bebb] text-6xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Keynote Speaking
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Engaging and impactful speeches designed to inspire, motivate, and
            empower diverse audiences at corporate events, conferences, and
            seminars. Topics are customized to align with your event's theme and
            objectives.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-[#14a4a0] hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            Book a Keynote
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-[#1a2b3a] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="text-yellow-400 text-6xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Business Coaching
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Personalized one-on-one or group coaching for entrepreneurs,
            executives, and teams. We provide strategic guidance to enhance
            leadership, optimize operations, and achieve significant business
            growth.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-[#14a4a0] hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            Start Coaching
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-[#1a2b3a] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="text-[#17bebb] text-6xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Workshops & Training
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Interactive and hands-on sessions designed to equip individuals and
            teams with practical skills in communication, sales, personal
            effectiveness, leadership, and strategic planning.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-[#14a4a0] hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            Request a Workshop
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-[#1a2b3a] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="text-yellow-400 text-6xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Online Courses
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Flexible and comprehensive digital programs covering core success
            principles, mindset mastery, and practical business strategies,
            accessible anytime, anywhere at your own pace.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/courses"
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-[#14a4a0] hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            View Courses
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-[#1a2b3a] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="text-[#17bebb] text-6xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Global Events & Seminars
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Participate in large-scale motivational events and public seminars.
            These events foster a community of growth, provide deep insights,
            and offer unique networking opportunities.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/events"
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-[#14a4a0] hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            See Events
          </a>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-[#1a2b3a] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="text-yellow-400 text-6xl mb-6">
            <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Mindset Development
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Specialized programs focused on cultivating a positive, resilient,
            and growth-oriented mindset. Learn to overcome mental blocks,
            enhance focus, and unlock your full potential.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-[#14a4a0] hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div
      class="book-appointment w-full px-5 bg-[#121a26] flex justify-center py-10"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-[#1a2b3a] px-8 py-8 rounded-2xl text-center shadow-lg w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6"
      >
        <div class="heading-a">
          <h2 class="text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins">
            Ready to Transform Your Life or Business?
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="btn w-full md:w-auto">
          <button
            class="bg-[#17bebb] text-white text-base md:text-xl px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold cursor-pointer transition-all ease-in-out hover:bg-[#139a94] hover:scale-105 w-full md:w-auto"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>

    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b47dbbf1c5.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>

    <script src="/JS/mobileresponsive.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
